<a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-u5aZz5ZT29M/UUdgc0zNvPI/AAAAAAAABaY/2BE3QSFk5Eo/s1600/HubSpot_logo_255x588.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"86\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-u5aZz5ZT29M/UUdgc0zNvPI/AAAAAAAABaY/2BE3QSFk5Eo/s200/HubSpot_logo_255x588.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></a></div>
